    <h3 style="color: var(--success); margin-top: 0;">Important Information</h3>
    <p style="margin-bottom: 0;">Your account is now fully operational. You can log in using your Client ID and the password you created during registration. If you haven't set a password yet, please use the 'Forgot Password' option on the login page.</p>
</div>

<h2>Your Account Details</h2>

<div class="account-details">
    {{> detail-row label="Client ID" value=clientId}}
    {{> detail-row label="Account Number" value=accountNumber}}
    {{> detail-row label="Account Type" value=accountType}}
    {{> detail-row label="Activation Date" value=activationDate}}
    {{> detail-row label="Account Status" value="Active" valueStyle="color: var(--success); font-weight: 600;"}}
